 drivers/gpu/drm/msm/dsi/dsi.c         | 10 +++++++---
 drivers/gpu/drm/msm/dsi/dsi.h         |  1 -
 drivers/gpu/drm/msm/dsi/dsi_manager.c | 17 -----------------
